            </span>
            <span id="Contributor_Name_Mod">
            teresa roos
            </span>
            <span id="First_Paragraph_Mod">
              We were privileged to serve in the Idaho Boise mission office. My calling was the baptismal secretary. I had other jobs that I did in the mission, too, but that was my main calling. I recorded the baptisms and transmitted them to Salt Lake so that those new members would be able to become members of the Church. They were not actually a member until their membership was recorded in the Church.
            <br />
            </span>
            <div id="boxmodex3" class="clearfix">
                <div class="ChapterVideoDivMod">
                    <div class="ChapterVideoMod">
