            </span>
            <span id="First_Paragraph_Mod">
           In 1993, Bill retired from the Veterans Service and we flew up to Boise looking for a home in Boise. But we didn’t find a home in Boise, so we came over to Caldwell and found a house here. We retired, rented a truck, and moved everything we had in that truck to Caldwell.
            <br />
            </span>
            <div id="boxmodex3" class="clearfix">
                <div class="ChapterVideoDivMod">
